<div style="width: 600px; max-height: 550px; overflow-x: auto;"><h1 class="green b_mar_ten">ECCC SPOTLIGHT LOUNGE PRESENTS: SECRET ORIGINS WITH CHRIS CLAREMONT</h1>
	<p class="size11"><strong>Room: EMERALD CITY SPOTLIGHT LOUNGE (604)</strong><em><br/>Start: 2:40PM<br/>End: 3:35PM</em></p><br/>
	<p class="rte">Join host Blair Butler (Attack of the Show) as she talks to legendary comic writer<b> Chris Claremont</b>! Subjects are sure to include his unparalleled run of 17 years on "The Uncanny X-Men" and it's many spin off titles, his work with George Lucas on "Chronicles of the Shadow War" (which continued the story of Elora Danan from the movie "Willow") as well as his creator owned work, "Sovereign Seven", which was published by DC Comics in the mid 90's.<br></p></div>